### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api

### ========================================
### Employees API
### ========================================

### Get all employees (default: 1000 records)
GET {{baseUrl}}/employees

### Get employees with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/employees?skip=0&take=10

### Get employees - page 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/employees?skip=10&take=10

### Get single employee by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/employees/1

### ========================================
### Employee Details API
### ========================================

### Get all employee details (default: 1000 records)
GET {{baseUrl}}/employees/details

### Get employee details with pagination
GET {{baseUrl}}/employees/details?skip=0&take=10

### Get employee details - page 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/employees/details?skip=10&take=10

### Get details for a specific employee
GET {{baseUrl}}/employees/1/details

### Update employee detail (first_name, last_name)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/employees/1/details
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "UpdatedFirst",
  "last_name": "UpdatedLast"
}

